These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  journalist, dressmaker, engineer, designer, social-worker
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: gospel, house, trance, reggae, pop
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: poppy, marigold, lily, balloon-flower, rose
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, august, october, april, may
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 2. the fan trance is on the left of the dressmaker##1
 3. the fan pop is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 4. the engineer is the engineer##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is the fan gospel##1
 6. the social-worker is on the left of the engineer##1
 7. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growslily##1
 8. the designer is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 9. the designer is on the far right##1
10. the journalist is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
11. the social-worker is between the person who growsmarigold and the fan pop##2
12. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the fan house##1
13. the person who growsrose is on the right of the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Job      | journalist        | dressmaker | social-worker     | engineer   | designer |
| Music-Genre   | trance     | house      | reggae | pop   | gospel    |
| Flower   | balloon-flower  | marigold     | poppy | lily | rose  |
| Birthday           | august | october      | may     | april   | february     |

