.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: june, july, april, november, october
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, tennis, volleyball, snowboarding, water-polo
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: thriller, documentary, spy, sports, action
House: craftsman, art-deco, victorian, modern, tower
 1. the tower house is in the middle##1
 2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the tower house##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 5. the art-deco house is between the person watching thriller movies and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
 6. the modern house is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 7. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the craftsman house##1
 8. the person watching spy movies is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 9. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
11. the person watching spy movies is the person who's birthday is in april##1
12. the art-deco house is on the right of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Birthday         | november | june | october    | july  | april    |
| Sport   | water-polo    | tennis       | volleyball      | basketball | snowboarding        |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | documentary     | thriller    | sports  | spy     |
| House     | victorian    | art-deco | tower | modern | craftsman |

