.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
5 different pets are kept: horse, turtle, lizard, guinea-pig, pony
The people use 5 different means of transport: taxi, skateboard, motorbike, ship, roller
The people have 5 different jobs:  project-manager, librarian, firefighter, dressmaker, analyst
House: modern, victorian, craftsman, cape-cod, tower
 1. the owner of the pony is the librarian##1
 2. the cape-cod house is in the middle##1
 3. the dressmaker is in the middle##1
 4. the person driving the taxi is in the middle##1
 5. the owner of the pony is on the right of the victorian house##1
 6. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the project-manager##1
 7. the analyst is on the left of the craftsman house##1
 8. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the firefighter is on the far left##1
10. the modern house is the person driving the ship##1
11. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the tower house##1
12. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the analyst##1
13. the tower house is between the person driving the roller and the owner of the lizard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Pet         | horse | pony     | lizard   | turtle   | guinea-pig |
| Transport   | roller  | skateboard | taxi | ship | motorbike        |
| Job   | firefighter      | librarian      | dressmaker       | analyst       | project-manager       |
| House         | victorian | tower  | cape-cod    | modern    | craftsman        |

