.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: poppy, orchid, zinnia, lily, begonia
5 different games are played: backgammon, mah-jongg, poker, chess, go
5 different pets are kept: mouse, horse, snake, hedgehog, goldfish
The people have 5 different jobs:  architect, manager, bartender, mechanic, project-manager
 1. the manager is on the far left##1
 2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 3. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 4. the project-manager is between the owner of the hedgehog and the person who growslily##2
 5. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 6. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the bartender##1
 7. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 8. the person playing go is the owner of the horse##1
 9. the owner of the goldfish is in the middle##1
10. the owner of the hedgehog is the architect##1
11. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing poker##1
12. the architect is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
13. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Flower          | begonia  | zinnia     | lily   | orchid     | poppy |
| Game         | go | backgammon    | poker  | chess | mah-jongg   |
| Pet   | horse        | mouse    | goldfish     | snake     | hedgehog    |
| Job   | manager    | bartender | mechanic | project-manager | architect   |

