 3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 4. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person driving the quad-bike##2
 5. the person driving the van is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 7. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 8. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
 9. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
10. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
11. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
12. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
13. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1

