.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: d&b, hip-hop, reggae, house, gospel
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: azalea, amaryllis, sunflower, dahlia, marigold
There 5 different types of food: lime, cabbage, apple, papaya, banana
5 different pets are kept: rabbit, lizard, fish, cat, guinea-pig
 1. the person eating banana is between the owner of the lizard and the person eating cabbage##2
 2. the person eating apple is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
 3. the fan hip-hop is the person who growsdahlia##1
 4. the fan d&b is on the right of the person eating banana##1
 5. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the fan hip-hop##1
 6. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 7. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 8. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the fan hip-hop##1
 9. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
10. the person eating apple is on the far left##1
11. the owner of the fish is between the person eating apple and the person who growssunflower##2
12. the fan house is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
13. the fan reggae is on the left of the fan house##1

