 6. the gothic-revival house is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person playing scrabble and the person who's birthday is in december##2
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in billiardd-games##2
 9. the fan d&b is on the left of the person who's birthday is in billiardd-games##1
