.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
5 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, rabbit, horse, ferret
There are 5 different favourite colors: azure, yellow, lilac, ebony, brown
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: parkour, cycling, golf, sailing, handball
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: june, august, july, october, april
 1. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
 2. the person who likes brown is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's sport is handball##2
 3. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 4. the person who likes brown is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 5. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's sport is golf##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 7. the person who likes lilac is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 8. the owner of the horse is the person who's sport is cycling##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who's sport is cycling##1
10. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
11. the person who likes brown is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
12. the person who likes yellow is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Pet         | rabbit    | ferret  | chinchilla  | cat      | horse |
| Color   | yellow    | brown   | ebony | lilac | azure   |
| Sport   | golf | parkour    | handball    | sailing       | cycling         |
| Birthday   | october  | august | april    | july     | june      |

 